description:
Spiritual intimacy plays a role in your Christian walk, and getting to know God is possible! You can grow closer to God as you learn about His different names and titles. 

Watch this #short clip from the Global #Campmeeting sermon, “God’s Names: Unveiling Their Purpose and Significance in Our Lives,” https://youtu.be/C1dPCVOLF0g as Yvonne Shelton talks about the significance and purpose of God's names in our lives.
